Texts.Chs:
传统的牛肉。煮熟后味道会很好，甚至更好……当然得放在烧烤架上。通常它不是装在罐子里的，但有人想让它保质期更长。这种做法是值得怀疑的。
^orange;类型：熟肉食^reset;
Texts.Eng:
Classic beef. Would taste great when cooked or even better... grilled on a barbecue. Typically it doesn't come in a can. But somebody wanted to make it last. The cuts this came from are questionable.
^orange;Type: Cooked Meat^reset;
